narrative.title: Provider Overview
narrative.text: Wellnow Urgent Care, P.c. is a Clinical Medical Laboratory provider based in Syracuse, NY. From the 2018–2024 period, this provider received $33.1M in Medicaid payments across 690K claims.

narrative.title: Why This Matters
narrative.text: At $33.1M in Medicaid payments, this provider represents significant public healthcare spending. Understanding where these dollars go helps ensure the program serves those who need it most.
